    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require a dedicated owner ready for a significant project. The engine currently runs roughly and exhibits stalling issues, suggesting a need for a major overhaul or replacement. Cosmetically, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, and the interior shows heavy wear with several tears in the upholstery and a cracked dashboard. While it does move under its own power, it is not recommended for long-distance driving in its current state. This is an ideal candidate for parts or a complete ground-up restoration for someone with the right tools and expertise.",
      "price": 4800.0,
