    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in really solid shape and ready for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and has been well-maintained, making it a perfect, reliable choice for anyone looking for a great ride that looks awesome on the road. I'm sad to see it go, but I'd love for it to find a great new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
      "price": 32500.0,
