      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example delivers a visceral driving experience via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement, while the suspension retains its precision through refreshed bushings and dampers. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While displaying minor aesthetic patina indicative of its 'good' status, the vehicle\u2019s powertrain integrity and kinematic performance remain exceptional for the discerning driver.",
